metadata.name: Mẹ́rin
metadata.description:
This is our space, we are the
cosmic media
From our lips the universe
speaks
Telling stories long lost or truths
hidden
We are the four, the messengers
on all sides
We are there but unseen, we
make contact but are unreal
We are one with the earth, its
roots
Endless be our reach, dauntless
is our spirits
We are the four, 
we are Orígun Mẹ́rin.
